    Return the metadata of a dataset (package) and its resources.

    th_package_show.Rd

    Return the metadata of a dataset (package) and its resources.

    Usage

    th_package_show(package_id)

    Arguments

    package_id

    Package ID.

    Value

    a nested list.

    Examples

    th_package_show("3e9d9124-d187-4fc7-b2fb-22c681ceb4fe")
